{"tid":2274826,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件香港日常生活中嘅好人好事","createTime":"2020-11-06T16:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T16:38:42.000Z","uid":44423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7c5cb54588043141ce5926125bb1eb57b01194c8","tid":2274826,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:38:42.000Z","msg":"事源係<br />\n小弟我坐巴士(尾二班車)翻屋企<br />\n我一上車 拍八達通Sim卡 發現餘額不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住身上三張八達通(廢老卡 + Smart octopus + Sim ) <br />\n加少少現金 實比到錢搭車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n車門閂左 開左車<br />\n最後發現兩張卡都無錢 廢老卡會比兩蚊only所以唔用得<br />\n我銀包嘅cash返張100同500<br />\n唔捨得比100 然而部車已經開左幾個站<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我落車又唔係 唔落車又無錢比<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唯有攞住張100 問車啲人找散<br />\n一開始問左個啊叔佢無散紙<br />\n啊叔後面嗰個可愛妹妹我唔敢問(利申：我係毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就問再後面個姐姐找散<br />\n佢有散紙不過唔夠100<br />\n我見可愛妹妹 同 再隔離嗰個姐姐都有揾袋<br />\n最後可能都係無散紙 所以無出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我企左喺度 佢地都無出聲 <br />\n空氣突然安靜 我就好撚尷尬咁企左幾秒<br />\n再問姐姐可唔可以比張廿蚊我<br />\n我Payme返<br />\n最後姐姐直接比左廿蚊我話唔洗pay返佢<br />\n謝謝你 <br />\n謝謝啊叔 可愛妹妹 同另一個姐姐 <br />\n香港人真好<br />\n令我可以順利回家唔洗比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前好豪爽先會買M記加大 ( 依家無食好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n今次直接比廿蚊搭巴士 比多左$4.5 好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廿蚊比咗我又唔洗我Pay返 原本比肥龍等佢請唱K都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係幾咁貴重<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#277E 勿相認<br />\n#已落車<br />\n#請善用不推文回覆"}]}